United States: Repetition is the mother of wisdom
It becomes even comical, the effort hard with which Barack Obama, president of the reputation of wise, reproduced the strategy of his predecessor on the Afghan issue, which he regarded himself as well.
When he eventually leave sweat its doctrine so ardently expected, it turned out that he had been replicated carbon paper since the Iraqi scenario of three years ago.
Not content to use in the text several times the expression "as in Iraq, it has not hesitated, moreover, to use the title of Bush's speech of January 2007 as the title of his own speech:" a new way forward "
At the same time, he has personally criticized the idea of Bush to send new reinforcements in Iraq consumed by the civil war as "irresponsible and a disastrous decision in its consequences."
The following month, however, have shown that the strategy of Bush, who came to the recommendations of commanders of campaigns, was the only possible and likely success to the point that the newspapers currently do not speak at all of Iraq.
This has not enhanced the reputation of Bush, however, objectively speaking, it was left to his successor a final situation much more favourable than we could have hoped.
Barack Obama hopes that in Afghanistan, the miracle will happen again
It is the commanders of campaigns that have requested an increase in the military contingent, including the commander of the operation in afghanistan, general Stanley mccristal, which has severely criticized the reluctance of the White House despite the habits of subordination.
He asked 40,000 men in order to make the situation more favourable.
The president has hesitated for three months but in the absence of a better option, at least he had defrauded the General of 10,000 soldiers.
He has managed to stamp out the promise of additional 5,000 from Europe, even if it had about 10,000.
This brings the most problems throughout the strategy of Obama appears to be its intention to withdraw the armies of Afghanistan by 18 months and complete the whole process within three years. The entire doctrine of Obama raises more questions than it provides answers.
Many doubt the fact that an increase of half will bring the same fruit that progress in Iraq.
Despite the fratricidal wars in recent years, Iraqi society is relatively well organized and its leaders to honour the agreements.
The Afghan situation is distinguished by the opposite - we cannot rely on person and no Treaty is respected.
In these conditions, difficult to prepare Afghan security forces, accustomed to change leader from day to day depending on what suits them.
The political institutions, although based officially, will remain just window-dressing behind which will proliferate patriarchal ethnic relations.
It is particularly complex to balance the interests of various ethnic groups given the lack of clarity about the reports, which are further complicated by the Pakistani and Iranian influences.
Even the foundation of a "state quick to act", which is the basic goal of the operation, does not appear to be very real.
The time horizon of the strategy Obama was perplexed by his proactive approach.
In the past eight years, the situation in Afghanistan has worsened and she is currently on the brink of chaos.
Only a heart purely romantic and outside reality can be confident that small soldiers sent in the tumult of the war for "prompt return home" will bring a real miracle.
From a political point of view, set a date for the withdrawal of troops is purely irresponsible since the Taliban will consider the indirect admission of defeat.
The last NATO summit has shown that the will of Europeans to participate in military operations in Afghanistan is moving towards the negative.
European politicians do not know or do not want to explain to their constituents why security in Germany or Italy is linked to a war in the mountains of the Hindu Kush.
Another factor that can radically alter the situation is the evolution of events related to Iran.
If the situation continues to deteriorate and enhanced penalties have no effect on the Iranians, the Americans will face the very difficult issue of a resolution of the problem by the use of military force.
It will respond by example when, according to Obama, America will come to the victorious withdrawal of troops from Afghanistan.
Each solution of this type will, however, a dramatic reversal of the Afghan situation.
The only patch for Obama is the fact that there are still three years until the presidential elections and therefore there is still enough time for that it is working on a new strategy, if it proves to be a flop.
The leaders of the bank Goldman Sachs will receive more cash
Employees senior leaders of the US bank Goldman Sachs will no longer receive cash bonuses this year.
The company announced in response to strong criticism of its pay practices.
The group of 30 key leaders will receive shares instead of money, they will sell within five years.
The actions can be withdrawn to the leaders if they would take too many risks.
According to reuters, Goldman Sachs and leader of the effort to link the pay with long-term performance on Wall street.
I suppose that Wall Street is well aware of the global sense that, "said the former investment banker Douglas Elliott of society's takeover
The concern is in the details, he added.
The bank Goldman Sachs has become the target of criticism after being set aside almost $17 billion in premiums on the first three quarters of this year.
For the current year, the total amount of the premiums is likely to exceed $20 billion despite the measure announced today, according to Reuters.
With the arrival of the financial crisis, large bonuses in the banking sector have become a sensitive political issue in many countries.
Britain announced Wednesday that it intends to spend a single fee of 50 per cent bankers' bonuses in excess of 25,000 pounds.
France is preparing similar measures. "
This year women won the Nobel Prize in all areas except physics
These are five women, a record number, which have received today in Stockholm hands of Sweden's King Carl XVI Gustaf the Nobel Prize in the technical disciplines and literature.
In addition to the four scientists there was also the German writer origin Herta Müller.
Two American biologists, Elizabeth Blackburn and Carol Greider received with their compatriot Jack Szostak the Nobel Prize for Medicine for their research in the field of chromosomes.
The prize for chemistry was awarded to the Israeli Ada Jonath with the Americans Venkatraman Ramakrishnan and Thomas Steitz for clarifying the structure and function of ribosomes
The last winner received the Nobel Prize in economics, the American Elinor Ostrom with his countryman Oliver williamson, for their analysis of economic governance.
The only technical discipline that has not been winner this year was the physical.
The award was presented today to scientists Charles Kao for his research in the field of optical fibres and George Smith avecWillard Boyle for their invention of CCD chips, which are the basis of all digital cameras, fax or telescopes.
Each winner received the diploma, the Nobel medal and certificate of acquisition of the financial reward.
It reached 10 million Swedish kronor in each category. (approximately 1.1 million euros)
If one of them has several winners, they will share the reward them.
The much-anticipated Nobel Peace Prize has already been handed this afternoon in Oslo in Norway to US President Barack obama.
In his speech, acknowledged the controversial nature of his reward since it is only at the beginning of his career and that it is in addition to the head of a country engaged in two wars in Iraq and afghanistan.
In the discharge of its policy he added that in certain situations the war is essential to achieve peace, even if the price is high.
