A British computer programmer collects 45 226 euros annual gross and a French, 31, while a Spanish receives 24 000.
Similarly, a driver perceives 34 247 euros annual gross in England, 25 751 in France and 16 420 in Spain.
According to Trovit, the lowest paid in Spain is that of server, with 11 592 Euros annual net, followed by the seller, with 14 725 euros, and that of worker, with 15 667 euros.
